lead_paragraph: Leicester City will bank on the inside knowledge and goal threat of Porto's nemesis Islam Slimani ahead of their Champions League Group G clash on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Leicester Bank on Slimani Experience Against Porto-Ranieri
